data.description: Discover a perfect blend of elegance and comfort in this beautiful Wasilla home. As you enter, you'll fall in love the upgraded interior doors and stylish LVP floors. The reverse floor plan layout offers three spacious bedrooms and a full bathroom downstairs, each with ample storage.Upstairs, natural light and stunning mountain views fills the living room and kitchen, creating a welcomingatmosphere. The kitchen offers granite countertops, a breakfast bar with a built-in wine refrigerator, and a convenient coffee bar. A half bathroom is tucked in to the corner and adds convenience. The primary suite is a peaceful retreat with plenty of storage and a tastefully designed bathroom with heated floors and a luxurious shower. Outside you'll have plenty of room to live your Alaska dreams with the RV pad, shed, and simple landscaping. With its understated charm and thoughtful design, this home is sure to impress. VA Assumable with a 2.6% interest rate.
